 stupid inventions.

26
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:32,267
That's it, that's my
 life in a nutshell.

27
00:04:32,267 --> 00:04:35,367
- Well, maybe you can
 invent a girlfriend.

28
00:04:35,367 --> 00:04:37,533
- I'm being serious, Rudy.

29
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:44,333
- Josh, you've gotta
 lighten up a little.

30
00:04:44,333 --> 00:04:46,267
I mean, there's lots of

31
