undersized guys who achieved
 greatness and stuff.

32
00:04:52,133 --> 00:04:53,067
- Like who?

33
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,733
- Napoleon.

34
00:04:58,267 --> 00:05:02,433
- Well, that's great, if
 I want to conquer Europe.

35
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,400
- Spud Webb.

36
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:08,533
- He's an athlete,
 so it evens out.

37
00:05:08,533 --> 00:05:09,767
Girls don't care if you're short

38
00:05:09,767 --> 00:05:13,067
