 sports, and I'm not.

39
00:05:13,067 --> 00:05:16,533
- Okay, how about those midget
 guys from The Wizard of Oz?

40
00:05:16,533 --> 00:05:19,167
I mean, they seemed to do
 pretty good by themselves.

41
00:05:19,167 --> 00:05:20,533
They got to be in a movie,

42
00:05:20,533 --> 00:05:22,567
they got to wear
 those cool shoes.

43
00:05:22,567 --> 00:05:25,733
- Rudy, if you're trying to
 cheer me up, just forget it.

44
00:05:25,733 --> 00:05:27,333
I'm just gonna have
 to live with people

45
00:05:27,333 --> 00:05:29,733
