 pint" and "shorty" for
 the rest of my life.

46
00:05:29,733 --> 00:05:31,233
That's all.

47
00:05:31,233 --> 00:05:33,133
And Courtney Wilson's
 never gonna like me.

48
00:05:33,133 --> 00:05:33,967
- Whoa!

49
00:05:36,567 --> 00:05:38,367
Courtney Wilson?

50
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:41,100
The hottest senior
 at our school?

51
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:44,067
- No, Courtney Wilson
 the U.S. senator.

52
00:05:44,067 --> 00:05:46,867
Of course Courtney Wilson
 who goes to our school.

53
00:05:46,867 --> 00:05:48,300
It doesn't matter anyways.

54
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:50,233
She's never gonna notice me.

55
00:05:50,233 --> 00:05:53,233
Girls just don't
like short guys.

56
00:05:53,233 --> 00:05:54,133
- Says who?

57
00:05:55,933 --> 00:05:57,800
- They just don't, okay!?

58
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,467
They like big, hulking
 guys with muscles.

59
00:06:00,467 --> 00:06:02,367
