 really think that way,

60
00:06:02,367 --> 00:06:04,833
maybe you should
 aim a little lower.

61
00:06:04,833 --> 00:06:05,733
- Like who?

62
00:06:07,267 --> 00:06:11,067
- Well, there's crazy
Bertha, the lunch lady.

63
00:06:12,067 --> 00:06:14,233
(laughing)

64
00:06:16,233 --> 00:06:17,433
Wait!

65
00:06:17,433 --> 00:06:18,833
Wait, I haven't
 even got to the gals

66
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:23,067
at the old folks'
 home yet (laughs).

67
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:27,500
(school bell rings)

68
00:06:48,633 --> 00:06:49,467
Do it.

69
00:07:00,467 --> 00:07:04,167
- [Josh] There it is, first
 prize at the science fair.

70
00:07:04,167 --> 00:07:08,400
- Dude, if that was a chick,
 I'd marry her on the spot.

71
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,867
- Don't get too excited.

72
00:07:09,867 --> 00:07:13,433
