 the oxygen mix is dead on.

75
00:07:17,433 --> 00:07:19,067
- Oxygen mix?

76
00:07:19,067 --> 00:07:20,900
What does a model sub
need an oxygen mix for?

77
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:22,167
It's not like
somebody's really gonna

78
00:07:22,167 --> 00:07:23,900
ride around in it, right?

79
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:25,400
- Well, the whole
 point is to make

80
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,567
an absolute scale replica
 of a submersible, Rudy.

81
00:07:27,567 --> 00:07:29,967
