 just like the real thing.

82
00:07:29,967 --> 00:07:33,467
Real pressurization, real
 controls, and a real engine.

83
00:07:33,467 --> 00:07:34,800
The whole works.

84
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,067
If it's not like the real thing,

85
00:07:36,067 --> 00:07:37,267
well then we might
 as well have made it

