 with the experiment.

195
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:36,967
I mean, I could use
 some help, you know?

196
00:12:36,967 --> 00:12:40,500
- Yeah but sugar, I'm really
 bad at writing reports.

197
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,833
You're so good at it, you know?

198
00:12:42,833 --> 00:12:45,233
I mean, with football practice
 and trying to get everybody

199
00:12:45,233 --> 00:12:49,400
together for the party tonight,
I just don't have the time.

200
00:12:51,067 --> 00:12:52,467
I'm doing this all for you.

201
00:12:52,467 --> 00:12:55,367
You know that,
 don't you Courtney?

202
00:12:55,367 --> 00:12:56,567
- Really?

203
00:12:56,567 --> 00:12:57,867
- Absolutely.

204
00:12:57,867 --> 00:13:01,133
Nothing but the
 best for my girl.

205
00:13:01,133 --> 00:13:04,633
- Okay, I guess I
 can take care of it.

206
00:13:04,633 --> 00:13:06,100
- Hello.

207
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:09,533
Ooh, well, very
 impressive, Mr. Campbell.

208
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,433
You know, in all my
 years of teaching,

209
00:13:12,433 --> 00:13:14,433
I have never seen
 such a well-made

210
00:13:14,433 --> 00:13:18,067
or elaborately constructed
 science project.

211
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:22,067
Just between you and me,
 my man: You are a shoe-in

212
00:13:22,067 --> 00:13:24,933
to win this year's
 science award.

213
00:13:24,933 --> 00:13:26,667
- Thanks, Mr. Duncan.

214
00:13:26,667 --> 00:13:29,600
- You know, it kind of
 reminds me, when I was

215
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:32,167
a young high school science
 student like yourself,

216
00:13:32,167 --> 00:13:33,867
I built my very own time machine

217
00:13:33,867 --> 00:13:35,800
in the first annual
 science fair.

218
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,433
- Wow, a time machine?

219
00:13:37,433 --> 00:13:38,400
- Yeah.

220
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,367
- Did it work?

221
00:13:39,367 --> 00:13:40,833
- No.

222
00:13:40,833 --> 00:13:42,533
But it took out about half
 a block of power lines

223
00:13:42,533 --> 00:13:44,200
when I turned it on.

224
00:13:45,333 --> 00:13:46,567
Gone, man.

225
00:13:46,567 --> 00:13:47,400
See ya.

226
00:13:55,233 --> 00:13:56,767
