227
00:13:56,767 --> 00:13:59,433
I mean, Courtney invited
 you to the party, big guy.

228
00:13:59,433 --> 00:14:01,367
The hard part's over with.

229
00:14:01,367 --> 00:14:04,700
- First of all, all
 my clothes look bad.

230
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,733
- Your clothes look fine, dude.

231
00:14:09,733 --> 00:14:12,367
