 hand, might be a problem.

232
00:14:12,367 --> 00:14:13,367
- Oh, ha ha.

233
00:14:14,533 --> 00:14:15,767
We have an hour till
 this thing starts

234
00:14:15,767 --> 00:14:18,333
and I look like
 my mom dressed me.

235
00:14:18,333 --> 00:14:21,067
