 psychological, Josh.

236
00:14:21,067 --> 00:14:23,200
I mean, nothing in your closet
 is gonna seem good enough

237
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:26,333
for Courtney as far
 as your brain goes.

238
00:14:26,333 --> 00:14:28,633
You just need to lighten
up and be yourself.

239
00:14:28,633 --> 00:14:30,833
And anyway, I might
 have a solution

240
00:14:30,833 --> 00:14:33,200
that might impress the ladies.

241
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,233
- Yeah?

242
00:14:34,233 --> 00:14:35,467
- Cell phones, dude.

243
00:14:35,467 --> 00:14:37,233
They had a sale on 'em
down at the Circuit Hut.

244
00:14:37,233 --> 00:14:38,700
I picked up a couple.

245
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:43,267
We each get one, and they
 are state of the art.

246
00:14:43,267 --> 00:14:46,200
- A cell phone's gonna
 make us look cool?

247
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:48,500
- Yes, Bob, I think we should
 set up a morning appointment

248
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:51,700
with the board members and
 put this deal together.

249
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:54,133
Hey, can you hold on a sec?

250
00:14:54,133 --> 00:14:56,333
Why hello there, ladies.

251
00:14:56,333 --> 00:14:59,233
Let me finish up this very
 important business call.

252
00:14:59,233 --> 00:15:02,400
Then I can properly
introduce myself to you.

253
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:04,667
- Rudy, we're 17 years old.

254
00:15:04,667 --> 00:15:06,400
I seriously doubt
