- Nobody move!

1284
01:17:23,867 --> 01:17:26,067
(beeping)

1285
01:17:28,200 --> 01:17:29,600
- There they are.

1286
01:17:32,700 --> 01:17:34,867
- Well, here goes nothin'.

1287
01:18:01,133 --> 01:18:05,300
- Oh man, this is the best
 dance party of my life.

1288
01:18:10,333 --> 01:18:11,600
- It's working!

1289
01:18:19,267 --> 01:18:22,667
- You may have saved your friend
for the moment, little boy,

1290
01:18:22,667 --> 01:18:27,167
