 back to normal size.

1297
01:19:08,400 --> 01:19:11,167
- Yeah, except for your clothes.

1298
01:19:11,167 --> 01:19:14,567
So, why did you take
 that formula anyway?

1299
01:19:15,867 --> 01:19:20,300
- Well, because I know
you only like tall guys,

1300
01:19:20,300 --> 01:19:23,433
and I was hoping that the
 formula would make me taller.

1301
01:19:23,433 --> 01:19:24,600
- What?

1302
01:19:24,600 --> 01:19:26,467
I love short guys.

1303
01:19:26,467 --> 01:19:27,300
- Huh?

1304
01:19:28,400 --> 01:19:30,567
How could you possibly
 like short guys?

1305
01:19:30,567 --> 01:19:32,633
- Because, silly, then
 I don't have to stand

1306
01:19:32,633 --> 01:19:34,967
on my tippy toes to do this.

1307
01:19:41,733 --> 01:19:45,667
- Well, I think our
 work here is done.

1308
01:19:45,667 --> 01:19:47,733
- I guess I should call
 the cops, get these jerks

1309
01:19:47,733 --> 01:19:49,833
and their bad wardrobe
 out of here, huh?

1310
01:19:49,833 --> 01:19:50,833
- We should.

1311
01:19:52,667 --> 01:19:54,500
Hey Josh, the sub's wrecked.

1312
01:19:54,500 --> 01:19:58,067
What are we gonna do
 for a science project?

1313
01:19:58,067 --> 01:20:00,167
- Boys, I am proud to inform you

1314
01:20:00,167 --> 01:20:03,067
you have won the
science fair hands down.

1315
01:20:03,067 --> 01:20:05,167
