1326
01:20:23,267 --> 01:20:25,667
- Should we tell him
 about the antidote?

1327
01:20:25,667 --> 01:20:28,200
- Nah, let's give
 him a few days.

1328
01:20:28,200 --> 01:20:29,633
Besides, I think he's
 gonna like the fact

1329
01:20:29,633 --> 01:20:30,800
that he's finally gonna get an A

1330
01:20:30,800 --> 01:20:33,067
in science class
without having to cheat.

1331
01:20:33,067 --> 01:20:36,933
- Aww, come on, what
 did I ever do to you?

1332
01:20:36,933 --> 01:20:38,767
Hey, don't kiss him!

1333
01:20:38,767 --> 01:20:41,500
What about our relationship?

1334
01:20:41,500 --> 01:20:44,133
We're still goin'
 out, aren't we?

